        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Comprehensive Southern Border Strategy Act</strong></p> <p>This bill requires the Department of Homeland Security to report to Congress a comprehensive southern border strategy. The strategy must include (1) an overview of current security risks along the southern border; and (2) an assessment of the barriers, technologies, and tools that are necessary to achieve and maintain situational awareness and operational control of the border. </p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
